title: Eddie Bo - The Best Of [flac]
description:
This long out of print CD (Hubbub CD16, 1997) is one of my favourites and I just have to share it. No doubt one of the best forgotten soul/funk treasures of the 60s. Enjoy!

Note: About flac - yes the files are big, flac is a lossless audio format, which enables you to make exact (well almost) copies of original CDs. Please don\'t whine about the file size. Just visit http://flac.sourceforge.net/download.html and get flac codec and front end if you want to extract the files to CD fromat. If you want to compress flac to mp3, there are several options, Google! Flac is great and it\'s free!
